{"title":"Ecuación de trabajo respiratorio-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Nefrología/Ecuación de trabajo respiratorio-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Ecuación de trabajo\\Nrespiratorio","guid":"8kucCopclI0rZ55jbKKWXA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"1. Introducción","guid":"NEwRCApKhtt7r_FXODtoSQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Definición de\\Ntrabajo respiratorio","guid":"ptjkBchxSrKJmVk1zD1nyQ","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• El trabajo respiratorio (W) es la energía necesaria para vencer las resistencias elásticas y resistivas del sistema respiratorio durante la ventilación (1).","guid":"ui5ptQ-9je7ESA2jC18bLg","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Importancia en la\\Nfisiología respiratoria","guid":"llGhRO4jblwvNI3kWpmbdg","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"• Es esencial para el intercambio gaseoso adecuado y la ventilación efectiva.","guid":"3z1s52lEBW2-qDvgZzUL1w","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"• Aumenta en enfermedades pulmonares, lo que puede llevar a fatiga muscular respiratoria y fallo respiratorio.","guid":"oeiE--QL9o-YuMKWExgoeQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"Componentes del\\NTrabajo Respiratorio","guid":"jLGCYJPfdgoV-BN-7BJyGw","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"• Trabajo elástico (W_el) → Determinado por la compliance (C) pulmonar y torácica.","guid":"JnPUKGkmD-GzFmhl27gsMg","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"• Trabajo resistivo (W_res) → Determinado por la resistencia (R) de las vías aéreas.","guid":"7YhSaeSdzI-LTBlA8MAcIA","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"Referencias","guid":"aXZJ3LzCfNOU_vP7fEVmxQ","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"(1) West JB. Respiratory Physiology: The Essentials. 10th ed. Philadelphia: Lippincott Williams & Wilkins; 2016.","guid":"X5YD7pqvspvj1X33CqvCxw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"0","text":"2. Componentes del\\NTrabajo Respiratorio","guid":"RTQFx6FtMeeXY3VerZXABQ","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"Trabajo Elástico","guid":"-IdoveMdqjttLq6lT1VjKQ","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• Definición: Energía necesaria para vencer las propiedades elásticas del pulmón y la pared torácica.","guid":"tVBX57qm9OkWGE6_dvKfZQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"12","text":"Trabajo Resistivo","guid":"BuVKTxPDc-jlvgryHentWg","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"• Definición: Energía necesaria para vencer la resistencia al flujo de aire en las vías respiratorias.","guid":"2axWZLI1cGHgGl5_WseP9Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"0","text":"3. Ecuación del Trabajo\\NRespiratorio (W)","guid":"MUOESezzSetDpe-tqmg2Hg","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"Referencias","guid":"_UnuYziAcLoXKSvQD4saOA","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"(2) West JB. Respiratory Physiology: The\\NEssentials. 10th ed. Philadelphia: Lippincott\\NWilliams & Wilkins; 2016.","guid":"lTNzTZv5kjTId62I0itY0A","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"(3) Levitzky MG. Pulmonary\\NPhysiology. 9th ed. New York:\\NMcGraw-Hill Education; 2018.","guid":"-AyUmZvQs0ZNjHA3TWrKQw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"0","text":"4. Factores que Afectan el\\NTrabajo Respiratorio","guid":"F11z_lIBpYqmZ9MqJvvgTw","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Compliance\\NPulmonar (C)","guid":"KSE6f65ael-9n9S54fbdaw","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"• Definición: Capacidad del pulmón y la caja torácica para expandirse.","guid":"zLWzgII-YEJsMOFn7nkBtA","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"• Factores:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"• ⬇ Compliance → ⬆ Trabajo elástico (Ej: fibrosis pulmonar)","guid":"iPTpg57vJf6VmdBvBfilNg","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"• ⬆ Compliance → ⬇ Trabajo elástico (Ej: enfisema)","guid":"IrvxpwWXTHZf16AcXoQd6g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"21","text":"Resistencia de las\\NVías Aéreas (R)","guid":"AEWLly-6pwMUC-NT6aETFg","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"• Definición: Oposición al flujo de aire en las vías respiratorias.","guid":"6jnqqwgFKQKPStyBvcNtHA","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"• Factores:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• ⬆ Resistencia → ⬆ Trabajo resistivo (Ej: asma, EPOC)","guid":"Ix2d93ctoVxIqs9gqNhIKQ","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"• ⬇ Resistencia → ⬇ Trabajo resistivo (Ej: broncodilatadores)","guid":"-vpE4KjBYjbQmfjnO3ez0g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"21","text":"Fuerzas\\Nde Fricción","guid":"dz9NbGTEdLDrTRcdRASJwA","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"• Fuerzas viscosas en los tejidos","guid":"4PRRjjwduzeyMdzxEu2AJQ","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"• Fricción del aire en las vías aéreas","guid":"ZVjxKyJM1j7btlZtg3Q5CA","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"21","text":"Volumen Tidal (Vt) y\\NFrecuencia Respiratoria (FR)","guid":"dJvb1bSs2DCnUf-zLHXv1Q","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"• Volumen Tidal:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"• ⬆ Vt → ⬆ Trabajo elástico","guid":"ahsaSMtQcDxCCFm30rt7_w","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"• ⬇ Vt → ⬇ Trabajo elástico","guid":"h6ZLWQcTAIyrR9JiNxXrjQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"35","text":"• Frecuencia\\NRespiratoria:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"• ⬆ FR → ⬆ Trabajo resistivo","guid":"z_F3emZxs2qHwKds8ZtmFQ","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"• ⬇ FR → ⬇ Trabajo resistivo","guid":"ejwVJrKwK9v--l5_gxlPCQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"21","text":"Gráfico de Presión-Volumen","guid":"A7VudBfG1rE9BnoQ3PCekA","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"• Área bajo la curva P-V → Representa el trabajo total realizado durante un ciclo respiratorio","guid":"sfJ42qmsQxQXl8rM2hVeLQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"21","text":"Referencias","guid":"zxA_9WS6X2gbkyttSZdbuA","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"(4) West JB. Respiratory Physiology: The\\NEssentials. 10th ed. Philadelphia: Lippincott\\NWilliams & Wilkins; 2016.","guid":"ICvnqEsk66eLSFnVaz72GQ","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"(5) Levitzky MG. Pulmonary\\NPhysiology. 9th ed. New York:\\NMcGraw-Hill Education; 2018.","guid":"E-RRf1yi-ZHUoZane1nG3A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"0","text":"5. Medición del\\NTrabajo Respiratorio","guid":"zT5tA2zTA_LwJiHcbOicjw","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"Métodos\\NDirectos","guid":"GCQXr2ZQjOVSgzIh8WUOLg","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"• Espirometría:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"• Mide volúmenes y flujos respiratorios.","guid":"vNZaIS9f81yVA53C61WIfw","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"• Uso: Evaluar  VT , FR, V (flujo respiratorio).","guid":"0rakO33XsfK_b7Wb9Xc5BA","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"49","text":"• Gráfico: Volumen-Tiempo y Flujo-Volumen.","guid":"xCbULIdonKM0vPPitnVzOA","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"48","text":"• Pletismografía:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"• Mide cambios en el volumen del tórax.","guid":"Wgxwlnh3v3WKFI0DOapV4g","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"• Permite calcular la compliance pulmonar y la resistencia de las vías aéreas.","guid":"cI0EjHlH2qnFvGoNDSzwdQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"48","text":"• Uso: Medición de Palv  y  Patm","guid":"HpQesHTpJuIM7ka9g1V8mw","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"47","text":"Métodos\\NIndirectos","guid":"SprJqgXgXuUYUjrH_nEWiA","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• Presión Inspiratoria y Expiratoria\\NMáxima (Pimax y Pemax):","guid":"e49UiNTO3foiwHNnILeOUw","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"• Evaluación de la fuerza de los músculos respiratorios.","guid":"lDvqjKgR-4Hv6CTFgdgv9Q","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"• Uso: Identificación de debilidad muscular respiratoria.","guid":"tsfMK06HDumeMeADpK46tw","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"57","text":"• Cálculo del Trabajo\\NRespiratorio (W):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"• Fórmula:  W = W elástico + W resistivo","guid":"ji55V0OmBuoT9jh9RGy-Sw","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"• Integración de las presiones medidas y volúmenes respiratorios.","guid":"vXzRRqSqGrfvWXxH2D3hLA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"47","text":"Equipos y\\NDispositivos","guid":"VP0aNv488yvI6VjwCidrEg","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"• Manómetros:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"• Medición de presiones\\Nintrarespiratorias.","guid":"RIJwaOUZYI-BesEKyvO-lQ","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"• Uso: Evaluación de P alvéolo,  Paw,  Patm.","guid":"oCXZR8_T1Qvo5UKTnsTeIQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"64","text":"• Turbinas\\Nde Flujo:","guid":"0SHRpfF23u0v7Sp6tRZy-g","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"• Medición de la velocidad del flujo de aire.","guid":"2ErgLILS6_8sJKScLNNH9g","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"• Uso: Cálculo de la resistencia de las vías aéreas y el trabajo resistivo.","guid":"4jiXqCJWgU0D9pi0V1Hl9Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"47","text":"Importancia\\NClínica","guid":"nEPmfbE2CqUoa6vJZVgXKA","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"• Evaluación del estado funcional pulmonar en enfermedades crónicas.","guid":"XoOKaBojER06soglgqo_Dw","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"71","text":"• Monitorización en pacientes críticos y con ventilación mecánica.","guid":"NyEpWnLK8s7Mc-jpceFnhw","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"71","text":"• Diagnóstico y manejo de patologías que aumentan el trabajo respiratorio.","guid":"nHnvYsTaV1FawIJyO0wIYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"47","text":"Referencias","guid":"5Qq8ogYBvnfxH2oGbMfbWw","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"(6) West JB. Respiratory Physiology: The\\NEssentials. 10th ed. Philadelphia: Lippincott\\NWilli