dren":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"89","text":"• Medición del W:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"89","text":"• Evaluación de la carga de\\Ntrabajo del paciente.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"89","text":"• Ajuste de soporte\\Nventilatorio según necesidad.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"78","text":"Impacto en la\\NVentilación Mecánica","guid":"6UJe8Gg0bt_2WVzduXARfQ","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"• Modos Ventilatorios:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"• Ventilación controlada\\Npor volumen (VCV):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"96","text":"• Control preciso de  V_T , puede ⬆\\NW_el si la compliance es baja.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"96","text":"• Ventilación controlada\\Npor presión (PCV):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"96","text":"• Ajuste de  P_{inspiratoria} , puede ⬇\\NW_res en caso de alta resistencia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"96","text":"• Estrategias de\\NProtección Pulmonar:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"96","text":"• Uso de volúmenes tidales bajos (\\NV_T ) para ⬇ daño pulmonar\\Ninducido por ventilación.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"96","text":"• Optimización de PEEP para ⬆\\Noxigenación y ⬇ colapso alveolar.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"78","text":"Referencias","guid":"n3hNiE4MY1VDpvWfP5omAw","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"(8) West JB. Respiratory Physiology: The\\NEssentials. 10th ed. Philadelphia: Lippincott\\NWilliams & Wilkins; 2016.","guid":"M8Buu-E9RRrMo9ZJIo4R2Q","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"(9) Levitzky MG. Pulmonary\\NPhysiology. 9th ed. New York:\\NMcGraw-Hill Education; 2018.","guid":"2D9OxLUN1L0vqA14-Rc6mQ","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"(10) Brochard L, et al. “Mechanical Ventilation in\\NAcute Respiratory Distress Syndrome.” American\\NJournal of Respiratory and Critical Care Medicine.\\N2017;195(4):577-583.","guid":"SVHCAO6xrtu4HLl6XzSgcw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"0","text":"7. Estrategias para Reducir el\\NTrabajo Respiratorio","guid":"oaZgrn_20RglcdXysTFQrg","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"Optimización de la\\NVentilación Mecánica","guid":"voP5r4jzTtO5GyVvqpI6TQ","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"• Volúmenes Tidales\\NBajos (VT):","guid":"jppKDizCocBjCjC1HB-vmA","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"• Uso: ⬇ daño pulmonar y Wel.","guid":"-7sMA0OHh5LdNmOetrtsOQ","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"111","text":"• Valor típico: 4-6 mL/kg de peso ideal.","guid":"VYcfttcQIXpwKlUH481BMA","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"110","text":"• Presión Positiva al Final de\\Nla Espiración (PEEP):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"• Uso: Mantener alveolos abiertos, ⬇ colapso alveolar.","guid":"qUQpq0nVKazml_EV7asGtQ","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"114","text":"• Beneficio: ⬇ Wres en pacientes con síndrome de dificultad respiratoria aguda (SDRA).","guid":"Ed_eEv5QXCHs2K5DzUHfRw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"109","text":"Uso de\\NBroncodilatadores","guid":"M6FIQFiHLYJwO5EcyuhiVA","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"• Tipos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"• Agonistas β2-adrenérgicos: (Ej: salbutamol)","guid":"4OQNkjFbEMHErzdBbhh07A","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"• Anticolinérgicos: (Ej: ipratropio)","guid":"zjKQU1ggjf9Z4-AsqbVX2A","children":[]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"117","text":"• Efecto:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"• ⬇ Resistencia de las vías aéreas → ⬇ Wres.","guid":"9r5GBKrf3HtrqdRRuc54Lw","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"• Mejora del flujo aéreo y ventilación.","guid":"WcYlBvy41g3rnl9vwUKYCQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"109","text":"Manejo de\\NSecreciones","guid":"au--EjQBsFjJmOIK041MHw","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"• Técnicas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"• Fisioterapia respiratoria: Drenaje postural, percusión.","guid":"IJYMxRc3QtlNLVOEJuEkrQ","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"• Aspiración traqueal: Eliminación de secreciones acumuladas.","guid":"Ch3catgXtuAz40AHNSGdqw","children":[]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"124","text":"• Efecto:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"• ⬇ Obstrucción de las vías aéreas → ⬇ Wres.","guid":"LS4z2pF_C6HTvbIlpYmnaQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"130","parent":"109","text":"Soporte Ventilatorio\\NNo Invasivo (VNI)","guid":"MVTam0QZPBaSzieHF5SBQA","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"• Modalidades:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"• CPAP (Presión Positiva Continua en la Vía Aérea):","guid":"VhpfqiggZ2Q_shnRTQu3AA","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"• Mantiene vías aéreas abiertas, mejora oxigenación.","guid":"gzFTpE-BcElVJsPhj4Mn5w","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"• BiPAP (Presión Positiva Bifásica):","guid":"L2R0nzGqIvjHDub7DimizA","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"• Ofrece dos niveles de presión, ⬇ Wres y Wel.","guid":"PaU6X1Rqmjyeh-2q8CJtYA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"109","text":"Terapias\\NFarmacológicas","guid":"S0cPYDlPPZKI58CWkakWkQ","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"• Corticosteroides:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"138","parent":"137","text":"• Uso: Reducción de la inflamación en vías aéreas.","guid":"VtHiOrceRQ-yPnyLdkvZfA","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"137","text":"• Efecto: ⬇ Edema y secreciones → ⬇ Wres.","guid":"Tw76ZFQh030pYlJzTi3OYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"136","text":"• Mucolíticos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"• Uso: ⬇ viscosidad de secreciones.","guid":"t6HgBNgki2Y8Tlw_6OFPUw","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"• Ejemplo: N-acetilcisteína.","guid":"MC_8P1Fm10q0ne3oYsw2YQ","children":[]}]}